# Local-only research inputs & third-party material — never committed.
# Reason: copyright + repo bloat. The product ships only paraphrased knowledge_base
# cards, never these source books, PDFs, spreadsheets, or competitor screenshots.
# Keep these on disk / private storage, not in git.
/Book and Articals/
/sources/
/Apps/
/archive/

# Temp previews extracted from copyrighted books
/_tmp_*/
/tmp/

# Local motion-card animation previews (the app ships optimized JPG cards)
/prototype_stage5_ua/assets/motion_cards/*.mp4
/prototype_stage5_ua/assets/motion_cards/*.webm

# Stray binary blobs anywhere in the tree
*.zip
*.pdf
*.doc
*.docx
*.xlsx
